helpText:
🤖 **Available Commands:**

• <prefix>start | <prefix>help
- `show the help for commands`

• <prefix>mode | <prefix>switch
- `switch the stream mode (audio/video)`

• <prefix>p | <prefix>play [song name | youtube link]
- `Gaana chalane ke liye ya queue me jodne ke liye`

• <prefix>radio | <prefix>stream [radio url | stream link]
- `YouTube live stream karne ka ho to ye command dalne ka`

• <prefix>pl | <prefix>playlist [youtube playlist link]
- `YouTube ka pura playlist chalane ke liye`

• <prefix>skip | <prefix>next
- `queue ka alge gaane pe Jane ke liye`

• <prefix>m | <prefix>mute
- `meri bolti band krne ke liye`

• <prefix>um | <prefix>unmute
- `band bolti wapis kholne ke liye`

• <prefix>ps | <prefix>pause
- `chalte gaane ko rokne ke liye`

• <prefix>rs | <prefix>resume
- `ruke gaane ko chalane ke liye`

• <prefix>list | <prefix>queue
- `queue ke sare gaane dekhne ke liye`

• <prefix>mix | <prefix>shuffle
- `queue ko shuffle up krne ke liye`

• <prefix>loop | <prefix>repeat
- `gaana loop pe chalane ke liye`

• <prefix>ip | <prefix>import
- `exported file ka queue import krne ke liye`

• <prefix>ep | <prefix>export
- `queue psnd aaye to future ke liye export krne ke liye taki Baad me upar wale import command se fir sun sake`

• <prefix>stop | <prefix>leave
- `khtm..tata..bye bye... Gya
